Usage example: !note add {@user/ID} {note}, !note del {@user/ID}, !note {@user/ID}
Requirements: 
Variables: UserNotes (value: <&#!0. ) ---include space after "0."
Command language: BDScript Unstable

Command trigger: !note
Code:

$onlyPerms[managemessages;Missing permissions: `MANAGE_MESSAGES`]
$onlyBotPerms[managemessages;Missing permissions: `MANAGE_MESSAGES`]
$nomention $suppressErrors
$if[$noMentionMessage==]
$if[$message[1]==]
$title[**!note info**]
